Hello, this is team 2647 and we are having trouble programming for the autonomous code for our robot.
We are new to programming so we really need help on this
Our team only has two coders including me and we are both new to this. we are trying to get programming going from the ground up.

edit:
-we are doing command based java programming for our robot
-we need to code for an arm, the drivetrain, and a gripper to work autonomously
-As far as I know, we do not have encoders for our team
-we are programming on VS code 2023
